text: Evelina Traykova (; born 2 November 1986) is a Bulgarian footballer who plays as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Bulgaria women's national team. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Bulgarian women's footballers Category:Bulgaria women's international footballers Category:FC NSA Sofia players
